{"3301610": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Streamer Manager Simulator 💖", "steam_appid": 3301610, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/extras/9c9b5aa4f4c29607b60935c1804ef29a.avif?t=1740324194\" width=630 height=168 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💟 故事 💟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切始於一個簡單的提議——幫助你的鄰居，渴望成為主播的Kaname實現成功。然而，隨著你在這條道路上越走越遠，你開始意識到她對名聲的夢想需要的遠不止魅力和一部相機。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/extras/d17029cb08ba8525fa4637c1911febe0.avif?t=1740324194\" width=630 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaname是一個藏有許多秘密的女孩，這些秘密隱藏在她的銀幕形象背後。在現實生活中，她是內向且害羞的，但在鏡頭前，她變成了一位星星，願意採取大膽的步驟來吸引觀眾的注意和認可。隨著時間的推移，你幫助她突破界限，提出越來越明確和挑釁的新直播格式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的行動和決策將影響Kaname的職業生涯以及你們的關係。你準備好幫助她飛向人氣的巔峰，還是會在半路停下？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能帶領Kaname走向成功，幫助她獲得她一直夢想的認可和名聲嗎？還是這條路對你們倆來說都太困難？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💟 核心遊戲玩法 💟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>直播管理：</strong>參與管理主播的日常生活——選擇直播主題，積極監控直播過程中的聊天室，封鎖仇恨者，參加有趣的小遊戲以提升觀眾參與度。實時跟踪Kaname的成功！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/extras/f3c566441d693f39b0b7adba503fcad2.avif?t=1740324194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/extras_big/f3c566441d693f39b0b7adba503fcad2.avif?t=1740324194 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>社交媒體：</strong>通過選擇吸引人的照片來管理Kaname的社交媒體頁面，吸引粉絲並提升她的受歡迎程度。回復評論，與她日益增長的觀眾互動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >服裝購買：通過為Kaname購買性感服裝來增添直播的色彩，這些服裝可以用來創造更具挑釁性的內容並提高觀看率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狀態管理：密切關注Kaname的疲勞、情緒和性感指數，以平衡她的職業和個人需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/extras/bbe1cd6c3fc26133eef572f15bbf57b5.avif?t=1740324194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/extras_big/bbe1cd6c3fc26133eef572f15bbf57b5.avif?t=1740324194 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💟 遊戲特點 💟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互動角色發展：</strong>選擇Kaname如何在直播界發展——從簡單的秀到更具挑釁性的廣播，影響她的受歡迎程度和個人成長。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>關係與情感：</strong>你的行動會直接影響你與Kaname的關係——你可以選擇讓你們更加親近，或是因你的決策而讓她感到疏遠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主播的日常生活：</strong>照顧Kaname，幫助她應對挑戰，並在她尋找自己的聚光燈位置時支持她。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互動場景與CG：</strong>欣賞精美的動畫場景，這些場景反映了Kaname的受歡迎程度上升以及她與你的個人生活的演變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/extras/d9ea192447f20922ebf5cfd0dfc67175.avif?t=1740324194\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/extras_big/d9ea192447f20922ebf5cfd0dfc67175.avif?t=1740324194 width=800 height=212 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301610/e